Summary: UFO examining jet chem-trail, disappears from plain sight.

divs: sighting detailsmy friend & i were traveling north on i5 near ferndale. i was looking at a southbound jet w\chem-trail & thought, "with all the reports of ufos checking this out, wouldn't it be funny.." and there one was! i witnessed it for roughly a minute. it was traveling slowly to the west. all of the sudden, it phased out of sight. it was a clear day. no cloulds & very bright.
